{"tid":197422,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖］［你問我盡量答］十個半月中南美 加 南極 ，而家仍在旅途中","createTime":"2017-04-12T00:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T00:39:18.000Z","uid":102368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75c49d6e5a0a5c24861c233fed539d82bd9c7130","tid":197422,"uid":102368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T00:34:10.000Z","msg":"來來去去都係日本歐洲遊記，係時候轉下口味講下南美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說小弟舊年五月尾香港出發，一路由<br />\n<br />\n古巴 - 墨西哥 - 哥倫比亞 - 厄瓜多爾 - Galapagos （進化島）- 秘魯 - 玻利維亞 - 智利 - 阿根廷 - 南極 - 烏拉圭 - 而家人在巴西 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n遊記不定期更新，有關南美都可以問／討論，你問我盡量答 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先來古巴 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5B1JfvN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5B1JfvN.jpg&h=7f269f56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相信大家對於古巴既印象一定有佢地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHavana 街景<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/He9z19G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHe9z19G.jpg&h=877466cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i191o93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi191o93.jpg&h=648215b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國會大樓<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/89080Rn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F89080Rn.jpg&h=3a6bcc81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHavana 人獨有既買野方法，所以話懶人總係特別多計<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9VyH423.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9VyH423.jpg&h=46a43ac7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n古巴自從幾年前開放網路俾民眾，古巴人同外界接觸就容易好多，每個城市既Wifi Zone 都總會見到一堆低頭族。雖然價錢不便宜，但自由無價！（OK , 自由價錢係：CUC$2 一個鐘！！） <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/81PKHcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F81PKHcd.jpg&h=62ee4a23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e22d44124dc11df6db1ce489ecee827e7fde1677","tid":197422,"uid":7852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T00:39:18.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}